Helpful tool for monitoring Twitch account information while streaming!
If anything seems a little rough, or if you encounter any bugs, please contact me at zclaycreationz@gmail.com.
You can also visit my website http://www.zclaycreationz.com/twitch-monitor/ for more information about Twitch Monitor.
Twitch Monitor is developed entirely in my spare time. Please click the 'Donate' button below to let me know you're enjoying the tool. Any help is greatly appreciated! :)
